  The Oscillation of the Linear Functional Equations
 
</article-title></title-group><contrib-group><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>戴</surname><given-names>丽娜</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff2"><sup>2</sup></xref><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff1"><sup>1</sup></xref></contrib><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>徐</surname><given-names>艳芬</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff2"><sup>2</sup></xref><xref ref-type="corresp" rid="cor1"><sup>*</sup></xref></contrib><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>林</surname><given-names>全文</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff2"><sup>2</sup></xref><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff1"><sup>1</sup></xref></contrib></contrib-group><aff id="aff2"><addr-line>广东石油化工学院理学院数学系，广东 茂名</addr-line></aff><aff id="aff1"><addr-line>null</addr-line></aff><author-notes><corresp id="cor1">* E-mail:<email>290773995@qq.com(徐艳)</email>;</corresp></author-notes><pub-date pub-type="epub"><day>22</day><month>07</month><year>2016</year></pub-date><volume>06</volume><issue>04</issue><fpage>327</fpage><lpage>336</lpage><permissions><copyright-statement>&#169; Copyright  2014 by authors and Scientific Research Publishing Inc. </copyright-statement><copyright-year>2014</copyright-year><license><license-p>This work is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution International License (CC BY). http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/</license-p></license></permissions><abstract><p>
 
 
   
   本文研究高阶泛函方程<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="Edit_4f1958e1-9661-4512-9b5a-abbbef1d8e9c.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula> 解的振动性，得到了一些新的振动条件，改进或推广已有文献的某些结果。  In this paper, we study of oscillatory of all solutions to the high order equation <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="Edit_21e0cf5d-75a2-4d04-8499-2c35ed9a7adc.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>We get some new vibration conditions, and improve or promote some of the results of previous literature. 
    
  
 
</p></abstract><kwd-group><kwd>泛函方程，解，振动性，非振动性, Functional Equations</kwd><kwd> Solutions</kwd><kwd> Oscillation</kwd><kwd> Non-Oscillation</kwd></kwd-group></article-meta></front><body><sec id="s1"><title>线性泛函方程解的振动性<sup> </sup></title><p>戴丽娜，徐艳芬<sup>*</sup>，林全文</p><p>广东石油化工学院理学院数学系，广东 茂名</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula481"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x8_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>收稿日期：2016年7月9日；录用日期：2016年7月24日；发布日期：2016年7月28日</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula482"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x9_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula></sec><sec id="s2"><title>摘 要</title><p>本文研究高阶泛函方程</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula483"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x10_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>解的振动性，得到了一些新的振动条件，改进或推广已有文献的某些结果。</p><p>关键词 :泛函方程，解，振动性，非振动性</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula484"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x11_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula></sec><sec id="s3"><title>1. 引言</title><p>考虑高阶线性泛函方程</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x12_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x13_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula> (1.1)</p><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x14_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>：<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x15_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是给定的函数，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x16_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是未知实值函数，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x17_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x18_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>上的一个无界子集，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x19_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x20_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>表示函数<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x21_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x22_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>次迭代，即</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula485"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x23_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>如果函数<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x24_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>使得<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x25_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>对任何<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x26_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>成立，且对<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x27_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>满足(1.1),则称其为方程(1.1)的一个解。这样的解称作是振动的。如果存在一列点<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x28_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，使得<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x29_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，且<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x30_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>对<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x31_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>成立。否则称为非振动的。</p><p>当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x32_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时，可得出文 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.18114-ref1">1</xref>] 泛函方程</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula486"><label>(1.2)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x33_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x34_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是给定的函数。</p><p>1995年，在文 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.18114-ref2">2</xref>] Nowakowska和Werbowski将方程(1.2)推广高阶线性泛函方程(1.1)<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x35_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的情形，得到方程(1.1)的所有解振动，如果</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula487"><label>(1.3)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x36_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>或</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula488"><label>(1.4)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x37_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula489"><label>(1.5)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x38_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>1998年以来，函数方程的振动性成为数学工作者研究研究的热门课题他们得到各类线性高级泛函方程和非线性高阶泛函方程解的振动准则(请参看文 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.18114-ref3">3</xref>] - [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.18114-ref12">12</xref>] ) (从略)。</p><p>2003年，文 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.18114-ref7">7</xref>] 研究了方程(1.1)的一种特殊形式</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula490"><label>(1.6)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x39_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>(i) 如果下面条件之一成立：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula491"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x40_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>或</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula492"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x41_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x42_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x43_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>在[0,1]上最大实根。则泛函方程(1.6)的所有解振动。</p><p>(ii) 如果下面条件之一成立</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula493"><label>(1)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x44_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula494"><label>(2) (1.7)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x45_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x46_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>由文 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.18114-ref7">7</xref>] (1.7)定义而<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x47_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>和<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x48_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>分别由引理2.1和引理2.2确定。则泛函方程(1.6)的所有解振动。</p><p>(iii)如果下面条件之一成立</p><p>(1)<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x49_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>,</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula495"><label>(2) (1.8)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x50_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x51_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>和<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x52_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>分别由文 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.18114-ref7">7</xref>] 引理2.1和引理2.2确定。则泛函方程(1.6)的所有解振动。</p><p>显然，当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x53_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，方程(1.1)变为方程(1.6)。本文在文 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.18114-ref7">7</xref>] 基础上，利用新的技巧进一步研究(1.1)，得到若干振动准则，我们的结果推广了文 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.18114-ref7">7</xref>] 的结果，改进了文 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.18114-ref1">1</xref>] ， [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.18114-ref2">2</xref>] 的某些结果。</p></sec><sec id="s4"><title>2. 引理</title><p>考虑泛函不等式</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula496"><label>(2.1)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x54_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>并令</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula497"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x55_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>在证明定理之前，为了简明首先证明以下引理。</p><p>引理2.1：假设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x56_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x57_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是泛函不等式(2.1)的一个最终正解，那么</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula498"><label>(2.2)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x58_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>这里<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x59_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是方程</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula499"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x60_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>在[0,1]上的最大实根。</p><p>证：从(2.1)容易看出</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula500"><label>(2.3)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x61_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>由于<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x62_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，所以当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x63_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时(2.2)成立。现在假设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x64_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，那么对任何<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x65_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>和足够大的<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x66_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，由<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x67_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，得：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula501"><label>(2.4)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x68_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>由(2.3)，有</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula502"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x69_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>迭代1次，有：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula503"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x70_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>迭代2次，有：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula504"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x71_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>迭代3次，有：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula505"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x72_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>根据数学归纳法，迭代<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x73_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>次，有：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula506"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x74_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>将上式代入(2.1)，并利用(2.4)得</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula507"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x75_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>以上不等式除以<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x76_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，只考虑不等式最左端与最右端，有：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula508"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x77_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>有：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula509"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x78_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>重复上面的推导，由归纳法，得</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula510"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x79_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>显然<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x80_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，此函数单调递减且有界，所以<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x81_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>存在，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x82_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，通过移项，令j趋于无穷，有：</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x83_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p>于是</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula511"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x84_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>令<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://ht