<inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x96_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时(2.5)成立。现在假设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x97_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，那么对任何<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x98_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>和足够大的<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x99_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，(2.4)成立，且</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula514"><label>(2.7)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x100_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>由(2.1)，令<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x101_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，有：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula515"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x102_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>等式两边同乘<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x103_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>有：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula516"><label>(2.8)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x104_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>对(2.8)从<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x105_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>到<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x106_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>作和，得</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula517"><label>(2.9)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250446x107_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>由(2.4)，(2.7)和(2.9)得</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18114-formula518"><graphic x